---
title: Caribbean-Style Chicken & Veggie Fries with Spinach Slaw & Aioli
description: We’ve packed the signature flavours of the Caribbean into this pork dish with mild jerk seasoning and a crunchy aioli
slaw, but we think the homemade veggie fries on the side might just be the best bit!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
